<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.4">
<l>uṭaiyārnta vāṭaiyaṉ kaṇṭikai yaṉuṭai nāṇiṉaṉ</l>
<l>puṭaiyārpoṉ ṉūliṉaṉ poṉmuṭiyaṉ maṟṟum palkala</l>
<l>ṉaṭaiyā vuṭaittiru nāraṇaṉ ṟoṇṭar toṇṭar kaṇṭī</l>
<l>riṭaiyār piṟappiṭai tōṟemak kemperu makkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with a dress that is full of cloth(?), he with a necklace, he with a cloth thread,</l>
<l>he with a golden string on [his] sides, he with a gold crown, he with many other ornaments,</l>
<l>Śrī-possessing Nārāyaṇa – the servants of the servants with him as [their] walk [of life], see,</l>
<l>are out great people for us in every birth full of troubles(?).</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
